name: FDJ01PenetrationAvoidanceFeeler
doc: Struct defining a feeler ray used for camera penetration avoidance.

AdjustmentRot: FRotator describing deviance from main ray
WorldWeight: how much this feeler affects the final position if it hits the world
PawnWeight: how much this feeler affects the final position if it hits a APawn (setting to 0 will not attempt to collide with pawns at all)
Extent: extent to use for collision when tracing this feeler
TraceInterval: minimum frame interval between traces with this feeler if nothing was hit last frame
